- `StateManager` has no `record_halt()` method yet
- `Runner` has no `_handle_impactful_error()` or `_in_emergency_flow` yet
- CLI has no signal handlers or exit code mapping yet

Every test will **fail** (red phase) until story 4.2 is implemented.

